==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*πόλις / polis / pol'-is

===Etymology===
*Probably from the same as [[πόλεμος]], or perhaps from [[πολύς]]; a town (properly with walls, of greater or less size): 

===Noun===
'''πόλις'''

# A [[city]].

